name: R4_spdx_license_for_R5
title: Cross-version VS for R4.SPDXLicense for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/spdx-license|4.0.1 for use in FHIR R5. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R4 to R5.
